          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1664882949651-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1664882949651-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pork mince is beginning to brown, crumble your <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> directly into the pan, add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until the mushrooms are starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1664882954513-x200.jpg",
