            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>spring onion whites</strong>,<strong> udon noodles</strong>,<strong> soy stock </strong>and a grind of<strong> pepper </strong>to the pan, gently separating the noodles with a fork as you add them to the pan</p><p>Cook, covered, for 2-3 min, stirring occasionally until the noodles are soft and coated in the sauce and the pork mince is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1664882965806-x200.jpg",
