            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the noodles have softened, remove the pan from the heat and add your<strong> toasted sesame oil </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>sesame</strong> <strong>pork & mushroom udon noodle stir-fry</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
