    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sesame</strong> <strong>pork & mushroom udon noodle stir-fry</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> spring onion greens </strong>and season with a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
